---
title: Quick Herby White Fish & Dijon Hollandaise with Steamed Veggies & Mash
description: Tender pan-seared fish never fails to catch our attention! It has all the familiar tastes of home cooking at its finest, plus a dijon mustard and hollandaise sauce and a side of beloved potato mash, this fish dish has our full attention.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
